Source: pg-uuid-v8
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), pkg-config, libssl-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/ineron/pg_uuid_v8

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-uuid-v8
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-uuid-v8
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: UUID v8 generator with embedded timestamps for PostgreSQL
  pg_uuid_v8 provides UUID version 8 generation functions with steganographic
  embedded timestamps for PostgreSQL.
